title: Army coach Monken says players adapting to virus disruption
description: Army football coach Jeff Monken sees a teaching point in all the disruption caused by the novel coronavirus
content:
Army football coach Jeff Monken sees a teaching point in all the disruption caused by the novel coronavirus.
